{"about_the_game":"<img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492430/extras/rw_steam_header1.png?t=1680651981\" /><br><br><strong>A quick note from the developers:</strong><br><br>Rift World Is a hardcore FPS game full of action-fueled magical encounters set in a surreal parallel world. You play as a young mage with a wanderlust for adventure, learning how to control raw sorcerous power and find a way through chaotic realms and hordes of fearsome enemies present within Rift World.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492430/extras/RiftCombat.png?t=1680651981\" /><br><br>On your way through each mysterious rift you will traverse difficult terrain and blast away your opponents with an ever-growing arsenal of magical spells - but beware, your magic needs to be utilized wisely. So drink your fill of potions, face massive foes and their bosses, and bring peace to the Rift.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492430/extras/RiftSpells.png?t=1680651981\" /><br><br>If you are thinking about buying Rift World, please keep in mind that this game was created by a small, but very passionate group of people. Each level was handcrafted for our players to escape into a world of magic and wonder.<br><br><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492430/extras/RiftMovement.png?t=1680651981\" /><br><br>We are constantly working hard on delivering the best experience possible for our players, so don\u2019t hesitate to get in touch with us if you have feedback, questions, or problems with the game - we\u2019ll do our very best to get back to you as soon as possible.<br><br><strong>This game offers you:</strong><br><br><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Fast-paced, exciting, and challenging gameplay </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Colorful, atmospheric, and handcrafted level design </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Destructible environment and scenery </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Numerous dynamic enemy encounters </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> Engaging boss battles </li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li> and of course... Magic! </li></ul>","achievements":{"highlighted":[{"name":"Magic Mushrooms","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/05154132825cba18e6a4d58e530d9cb5d30f7a9e.jpg"},{"name":"Gourds a Plenty","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/ac04bfc93ba84a051231baa06bf36902feef65d3.jpg"},{"name":"So Many Scovilles ","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/f2388a96076e8aa0d0491e8ea28c23ac7117dc1d.jpg"},{"name":"Let the Melons Sleep","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/7c1373ee29b1ee6e8ca977830fb043b5f37d9bc8.jpg"},{"name":"Vitamin A","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/a073de936ada3b4ba02b19550a96a64c72865abf.jpg"},{"name":"Spudtacular!","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/c3a89803dd1ce333dc34994d6ecfae24466aa919.jpg"},{"name":"Saucy","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/966d8dbbd3f24cb2d8953d8cab769c51d76dbaa2.jpg"},{"name":"I'm Not Crying, You Are","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/69205002bdb1f8cae616da061f3764eb8893c1a8.jpg"},{"name":"Ghost Broccoli","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/3c167622a2d51aedc9319acd1c33a09b5210722d.jpg"},{"name":"Eggcellence","path":"https://cdn.akamai.steamstatic.com/steamcommunity/public/images/apps/1492430/7bff49729bb9fe9734a4451533c61928161b73e2.jpg"}],"total":36},"background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1492430/pag